.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_SEND_STATUS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_send_status
.Nd send an XdndStatus message to a drag source
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft void
.Fn x11dnd_send_status "Display *dpy" "Window source" "Window target" "Bool accept" "int x" "int y" "int w" "int h" "Atom action"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_send_status
sends an
.Li XdndStatus
ClientMessage from
.Fa target
to
.Fa source .
This is typically called from within the
.Fn position_received
callback of a drop target.
.Pp
If
.Fa accept
is
.Dv False ,
.Fa action
should be
.Dv None .
.Pp
If
.Fa x
is 0, no status rectangle is reported (the entire window is implied).
.Sh RETURN VALUES
None.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_send_finished 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_register_target 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
